Change Coordinate Reference System so we can buffer in a unit other than degrees¶

Going to use UTM Zone 10 - EPSG:32610 - unit meters

In [ ]:
bridge_name_edge_buffers = bridge_name_edges.copy()
bridge_name_edge_buffers.to_crs("EPSG:32610", inplace=True)
In [ ]:
bridge_name_edge_buffers['edges'] = bridge_name_edge_buffers['geometry'].copy()
bridge_name_edge_buffers['geometry'] = bridge_name_edge_buffers['edges'].apply(lambda x: x.buffer(150))
bridge_name_edge_buffers.drop('edges', axis=1, inplace=True)
In [ ]:
bridge_name_edge_buffers_for_plot = bridge_name_edge_buffers.to_crs("EPSG:4326")
In [ ]:
